<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:38:12 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3ac482864a9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;漂亮的白色花束&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="White flowers including a few roses and greenery." height="912" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/phillycodehound/6a3ac482864a9.jpg" width="707"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://phillycodehound.some.pics"&gt;@phillycodehound&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:38:12 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>小星星</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3ac0546b698</link><description>&lt;p&gt;小星星&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A section of a meadow with common starwort (Stellaria graminea). The photograph has been edited so that the flowers appear to glow white against a very dark background. " height="2322" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a3ac0546b698.jpg" width="2322"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:20:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3abf5f5d016</link><description>&lt;p&gt;奥利夫正在做她最擅长的事。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Black curly haired Airedoodle laying on brown leather couch." height="2834" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/phillycodehound/6a3abf5f5d016.jpg" width="4542"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://phillycodehound.some.pics"&gt;@phillycodehound&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:16:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>未连接的点</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3a8632bede2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;点。未连接。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Closeup of a laptop keyboard. A red dot in between." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a3a8632bede2.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:12:21 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3a7421f1e61</link><description>&lt;p&gt;站在小区泳池浅水区边缘，低头看着“禁止跳水”的标志。我已经是会员有一段时间了，但去的次数并没有自己希望的那么多。今年，我想把游泳纳入夏季健身计划。这是很好的锻炼方式，也是多花时间在户外的绝佳借口。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='Bare feet standing near a pool edge with a clear "No Diving" sign in bold black letters. The blue water contrasts with the concrete surface.' height="2910" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3a7421f1e61.jpg" width="3886"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 11:55:19 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>